snippet.textDisplay:
Love you, Nikkie! You are 100% vrouw! You are 100% Nikkie! And as long as you and Dylan are happy, then that’s all that really matters.

Mine is a different struggle, but trapped is a good word for it. I’ve been trapped in a body that doesn’t work right. I contracted Lyme’s disease in 2011, went untreated for 5 years, and it disabled me to the point I completely lost my purpose in life. It’s taken a long time to figure out who I am now, and how to move forward, but since I got treatment, each year has gotten better, bit-by-bit. I’ve slowly been finding myself again and learning to love the new me. I’ve got lots of plans this year. 😊

Thank you for sharing your story. You are an amazing, beautiful, loving, kind, and inspiring vrouw. ❤️
